#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Empower your AI migrations to Quarkus with Skills"
msgstr "使用技能将人工智能迁移到 Quarkus"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Empower your AI migrations to Quarkus with Skills. Transform your AI agent into a framework domain: dependencies, jpa, web, etc expert capable of migrating Spring applications."
msgstr "使用技能将人工智能迁移到 Quarkus。将你的人工智能代理转化为一个框架领域：依赖、jpa、web 等专家，能够迁移 Spring 应用程序。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "What are Skills?"
msgstr "什么是技能？"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://agentskills.io/specification[Skills] are an open standard for packaging reusable instructions that teach AI coding agents how to perform specialized tasks. A Skill is simply a directory containing a `SKILL.md` file -- a Markdown document with YAML header describing what it does and when to trigger it, followed by step-by-step instructions the agent must follow."
msgstr "link:https://agentskills.io/specification[技能] 是一种开放标准，用于打包可重复使用的指令，教人工智能编码代理如何执行专门任务。一个技能只是一个包含 `SKILL.md` 文件的目录--一个带有 YAML 标头的 Markdown 文档，描述了它的作用和触发时间，以及代理必须遵循的分步指令。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Skills follow a progressive disclosure model that optimizes context window usage across all installed skills: agents load only the metadata at startup, pull in the full instructions when the skill triggers, and fetch reference files on AI's demand. This keeps context usage efficient while giving the agent deep domain knowledge exactly when it needs it."
msgstr "技能采用渐进式披露模式，可优化所有已安装技能的上下文窗口使用：代理在启动时只加载元数据，在触发技能时调入完整指令，并根据人工智能的需求获取参考文件。这样既能保持上下文使用的效率，又能在需要时为代理提供深入的领域知识。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Quarkus project maintains its own collection of Skills in the https://github.com/quarkusio/skills[quarkusio/skills] repository. These Skills transform a general-purpose coding agent into a Quarkus expert, capable of creating projects, upgrading versions, and -- as we will explore in this post -- migrating entire Spring Boot applications to Quarkus."
msgstr "Quarkus 项目在 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/skills[quarkusio/skills] 资源库中维护着自己的技能集合。这些技能将通用编码代理转变为 Quarkus 专家，能够创建项目、升级版本，以及（正如我们将在本篇文章中探讨的那样）将整个 Spring Boot 应用程序迁移到 Quarkus。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Why use AI Skills for migration?"
msgstr "为什么使用人工智能技能进行迁移？"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Migrating an application from one framework to another is a task that is complex and require deep knowledge about the technology used. Consider a Spring Boot to Quarkus migration: you need to rewrite the maven or Gradle build file, swap annotations (`@Autowired` to `@Inject`, `@RestController` to JAX-RS resources), convert configuration properties, refactor the Web layer to move to Qute, and more. Each of these steps follows well-known mapping rules, but the sheer number of files and the subtle interactions between them make manual migration tedious and error-prone."
msgstr "将应用程序从一个框架迁移到另一个框架是一项复杂的任务，需要对所使用的技术有深入的了解。考虑从 Spring Boot 迁移到 Quarkus：你需要重写 maven 或 Gradle 构建文件，交换注解 `（@Autowired` 到 `@Inject` ， `@RestController` 到 JAX-RS 资源），转换配置属性，重构 Web 层以迁移到 Qute 等等。这些步骤中的每一步都遵循众所周知的映射规则，但由于文件数量庞大，且文件之间存在微妙的交互，因此手动迁移既乏味又容易出错。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This is where AI agents shine -- they can apply transformation rules across an entire codebase methodically. But a generic agent lacks the framework-specific knowledge to make the right choices. It might produce code that compiles but does not follow Quarkus development best practices, or it might miss a critical dependency swap."
msgstr "这正是人工智能代理的优势所在--它们可以在整个代码库中有条不紊地应用转换规则。但通用代理缺乏特定框架的知识，无法做出正确的选择。它可能会生成可编译的代码，但却不遵循 Quarkus 开发的最佳实践，也可能会错过关键的依赖关系交换。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Skills bridge that gap. By giving the agent a curated set of instructions, reference mappings, and gate checks, you get the best of both worlds: the tireless execution of an AI agent guided by the deep domain expertise encoded in the Skill. The result is a migration that is fast, consistent, and with few errors."
msgstr "技能弥补了这一差距。通过为代理提供一套精心策划的指令、参考映射和关卡检查，你可以获得两全其美的效果：人工智能代理在技能中编码的深层领域专业知识的指导下不知疲倦地执行。其结果是迁移过程快速、一致且错误极少。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "How we designed the migration Skill"
msgstr "我们如何设计迁移技能"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The https://github.com/quarkusio/skills/tree/main/skills/migrate-spring-to-quarkus[migrate-spring-to-quarkus] Skill uses a:\n"
"- *Modular, domain-based approach* with *Gate checks*\n"
"- *Critical rules*: \"Never delete code you cannot migrate\", \"don't break the build\", \"Document every decision\", \"No silent changes\" aiming to safely migrate an application and to document the decisions made."
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/skills/tree/main/skills/migrate-spring-to-quarkus[从 Spring 到 Quarkus 的迁移] 技能采用了以下方法 *- 模块化、基于领域的方法，* 带有 *门检查* - *关键规则* ：\"切勿删除无法迁移的代码\"、\"不要破坏构建\"、\"记录每个决策\"、\"不做无声更改\"，旨在安全迁移应用程序并记录所做决策。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Such rules enforce how the migration process will take place and better express the needs than a generic prompt."
msgstr "这些规则规定了迁移过程将如何进行，比通用提示更好地表达了需求。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Rather than one monolithic script, the migration is broken into independent modules, each responsible for a specific technical domain:"
msgstr "迁移不是一个整体的脚本，而是分成独立的模块，每个模块负责一个特定的技术领域："

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Module"
msgstr "模块"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Responsibility"
msgstr "责任"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`jdk`"
msgstr "`jdk`"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enforce JDK 21+ compatibility"
msgstr "强制兼容 JDK 21+"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`build`"
msgstr "`构建`"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Migrate `pom.xml` or `build.gradle` -- swap Spring starters for Quarkus extensions, update plugins, adjust the BOM"
msgstr "迁移 `pom.xml` 或 `build.gradle` --将 Spring 启动程序换成 Quarkus 扩展程序、更新插件、调整 BOM"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`code`"
msgstr "`代码`"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Convert Spring annotations to their CDI/JAX-RS/Quarkus equivalents (`@Component`, `@Autowired`, `@RestController`, `@Repository`, etc.)"
msgstr "将 Spring 注释转换为 CDI/JAX-RS/Quarkus 的对应注释 `（@Component` 、 `@Autowired` 、 `@RestController` 、 `@Repository` 等）。"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`frontend`"
msgstr "`前端`"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Migrate Thymeleaf or JSP views to Quarkus-compatible alternatives and update static resource paths"
msgstr "将 Thymeleaf 或 JSP 视图迁移到与 Quarkus 兼容的替代方案，并更新静态资源路径"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`testing`"
msgstr "`测试`"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Convert `@SpringBootTest` to `@QuarkusTest`, replace `@MockBean` with Quarkus mocking utilities"
msgstr "将 `@SpringBootTest` 转换为 `@QuarkusTest` ，用 Quarkus 模拟工具替换 `@MockBean`"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`cleanup`"
msgstr "`清理`"

#. type: Table
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Remove leftover Spring artifacts, unused imports, and stale configuration"
msgstr "删除遗留的 Spring 工件、未使用的导入和陈旧的配置"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Each https://github.com/quarkusio/skills/tree/main/skills/migrate-spring-to-quarkus/modules[module] follows the same disciplined cycle: *Evaluate gate -> Load reference files -> Execute transformations -> Compile -> Verify*. A module only runs if its gate condition is met."
msgstr "每个 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/skills/tree/main/skills/migrate-spring-to-quarkus/modules[模块] 都遵循相同的规范周期： *评估门 → 加载参考文件 → 执行转换 → 编译 → 验证* 。模块只有在满足门条件时才能运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For example, the `frontend` module is skipped entirely if the project has no Thymeleaf or JSP templates. If compilation fails after a module completes, the agent stops immediately -- no cascading errors."
msgstr "例如，如果项目没有 Thymeleaf 或 JSP 模板， `前端` 模块就会被完全跳过。如果模块完成后编译失败，代理会立即停止，不会出现级联错误。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Different https://github.com/quarkusio/skills/tree/main/skills/migrate-spring-to-quarkus/references[reference] files help the AI model to better understand the transformations to apply:"
msgstr "不同的 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/skills/tree/main/skills/migrate-spring-to-quarkus/references[参考] 文件有助于人工智能模型更好地理解要应用的转换："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`dependency-map.md` -- maps Spring Boot starters to their Quarkus extension equivalents"
msgstr "`dependency-map.md` - 将 Spring Boot 启动项映射到其 Quarkus 扩展对应项"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`annotation-map.md` -- maps Spring annotations to JAX-RS, CDI, and Quarkus annotations"
msgstr "`annotation-map.md` - 将 Spring 注释映射为 JAX-RS、CDI 和 Quarkus 注释"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`config-map.md` -- maps `application.properties` / `application.yml` keys between frameworks"
msgstr "`config-map.md` - 在框架之间映射 `application.properties` / `application.yml` 关键字"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This design ensures that the migration is *transparent* (every decision is documented), *safe* (the build is verified after each phase), and *extensible* (you can add new modules or override reference mappings for your specific project)."
msgstr "这种设计确保了迁移的 *透明性* （每个决定都有文件记录）、 *安全性* （每个阶段后都会对构建进行验证）和 *可扩展性* （您可以添加新模块或覆盖特定项目的引用映射）。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-26-ai-skills-migration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "How to run a Spring-to-Quarkus migration"
msgstr "如何运行 Spring 到 Quarkus 迁移"

