msgid "The agent first scans the application using different tools executed locally and presents to the user a summary. Depending on which agent you use, the tools executed and the mode (code, ask, etc), the result will be different but nevertheless you should be able to see most of the information around a Java application as: JDK, Build tool, version, modules, etc."
